
Overview of adv bitterly

The adv bitterly has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (3) bitterly -- (with bitterness, in a resentful manner; "she complained bitterly")
2. (1) bitterly -- (indicating something hard to accept; "he was bitterly disappointed")
3. piercingly, bitterly, bitingly, bitter -- (extremely and sharply; "it was bitterly cold"; "bitter cold")
